Create Slicer 15

- Choose the Slicer from Visualizations ---> Drag the column to Field ---> Choose the Dropdown from type of Slicer.


Create ListName Slicer



Create Campaigns Slicer

- Choose the Slicer from Visualizations ---> Drag the CampaignTitle column to Field ---> Choose the Dropdown from type of Slicer.



Create Year Slicer

- Choose the Clustered Column Chart from Visualizations ---> Drag the SortDate column to Field ---> delete the Quarter, Month, and Day.

- Change the Clustered Column Chart to Slicer by clicking to the (1) Chart ---> Choose the (2) Slicer from visualizations ---> (3) Choose the Dropdown from type of slicer.




Create Month Slicer

- Choose the Clustered Column Chart from Visualizations ---> Drag the SortDate column to Field ---> delete the Year, Quarter, and Day.

Change the Clustered Column Chart to Slicer by clicking to the (1) Chart ---> Choose the (2) Slicer from visualizations ---> (3) Choose the  Dropdown from type of slicer.


Change the visualization of the Slicers

(1) Click to the Slicer

(2) Click to Format

(3) Click to Slicer Header ---> Turn off

(4) Click to Title ---> Turn On

(5) Change Title to List Name / Campaigns / Year / Month

(6) Change the Font color to “White” and the Background color to “Green”

(7) Choose the middle Alignment

(8) Change the Text size to “11”
